[37mThe question you are asking is really a societal one - and about operations that are like strip mining and waste dumping. [0m[37m[1m"Hunters and gatherers" (our genetic heritage) find fertile valleys, strip them dry and move on (this only works on a very small scale). "Civilization" is partly about learning how to overcome our dangerous atavistic tendencies through education and planning.[0m[0m[37m It's what we should be about generally (and the CS part of it is just a symptom of a much larger much more dire situation we are in).[0m[30m[1m - Alan Kay (2016)[0m[0m
